{"id":100,"count":2,"description":"Step back in time and uncover the rich legacy of Karnataka, a land where history, art, and architecture come alive. Explore the majestic ruins of Hampi, the capital of the Vijayanagara Empire and a UNESCO World Heritage Site, where ancient temples, royal enclosures, and stone-carved wonders narrate stories of grandeur. Witness the exquisite craftsmanship of Belur and Halebidu, with their intricately sculpted Hoysala temples. Walk through the regal past of Mysore, known for its grand Mysore Palace and cultural heritage. Discover the Islamic architecture of Bijapur\u2019s Gol Gumbaz, marvel at Badami\u2019s rock-cut caves, and experience the heritage charm of Bidar and Gulbarga. With its fusion of dynasties, monuments, and traditions, Karnataka offers a journey through centuries of history\u2014perfect for travelers who love culture, architecture, and timeless stories carved in stone.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/historical-karnataka\/","name":"HISTORICAL KARNATAKA","slug":"historical-karnataka","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/HISTORICAL-KARNATAKA.png","filesize":1000909,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"HISTORICAL-KARNATAKA-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":95251,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/HISTORICAL-KARNATAKA-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"HISTORICAL-KARNATAKA-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":20152,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/HISTORICAL-KARNATAKA-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"HISTORICAL-KARNATAKA-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":484305,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/HISTORICAL-KARNATAKA-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"HISTORICAL-KARNATAKA